&lt;li&gt;Oversee the timely closing of employee commitments through feeder vehicles; manage the setup of entities and partners within internal systems and the general ledger in partnership with Legal and GP Services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review new fund opportunities to ensure employee participation options align with firm policies and carry plan awards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a primary point of contact for senior internal stakeholders regarding commitment status, participation levels, and program mechanics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interface with external vendors and fund administrators to ensure seamless execution of employee onboarding and administration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, test, and own a new suite of co-investment, promote, and commitment reports in collaboration with internal Engineering and GPS teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
